{"h52c27b70gfa44g4094gb793gdd1d48eb47e0": ["He's gone. He's really gone. Connor...", "08c970d7-3138-45e8-8965-68eadf4b07cd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "c2fee0ae-7046-2258-69df-2dc445087e28"], "hdee1cc81g9babg4208gaf42gf95f2d26be64": ["I - I can't... get away. All of you just - just get away!", "08c970d7-3138-45e8-8965-68eadf4b07cd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "156be359-4e94-c10a-1fa6-afc3f1489245"], "h084cf424gb6e0g47e0gaa9ega795e30dd85d": ["Come back soon. <i>Please.</i>", "08c970d7-3138-45e8-8965-68eadf4b07cd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "26d95dc3-1a3e-a498-28b5-e736c772eb04"], "hef8299a6gde25g449agbbddgea7e5320069c": ["Where's the teahouse? What's going on? ", "08c970d7-3138-45e8-8965-68eadf4b07cd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "3d823df4-368d-0b70-ddf5-503a043e8586"], "h562f52bbg9864g4392gb1a3g95a07e4cdac4": ["An illusion - this is what it's really like.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "ee77096e-90a5-c57d-fc4e-f103727188fb"], "h56f65370g71a1g4f57gbbe6g34cd5d76c836": ["What? But the house -", "08c970d7-3138-45e8-8965-68eadf4b07cd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "dc5d6d08-6672-9547-0bed-32fd5d82434f"], "h61343169geb61g42a6g8481g0d59aba26951": ["Gods, this place! ", "08c970d7-3138-45e8-8965-68eadf4b07cd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "bd418c94-7208-c758-0e82-5125056100ac"], "h0be9c634gbbbcg450fgb41ag0c70e4f2e4e0": ["Stay put. I'll be back soon. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "338f7fe4-8011-9bae-7c71-bdb411c5863c"], "h0d7754aeg5613g46aag881fgf217121a4683": ["Please don't leave me here. ", "08c970d7-3138-45e8-8965-68eadf4b07cd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "bb8a9808-d944-b95f-919d-29a7918ae9b0"], "h6e5403b8g5ffbg4ef6g8f24g56ccf55bf3fb": ["Leave this place. Never come back.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "6fd3d40e-bffc-f9be-5090-c2eb4c98d4e7"], "hcb0e0205gc999g46a0gbbb2g01c1122977db": ["On my own? No. I <i>can't. </i>", "08c970d7-3138-45e8-8965-68eadf4b07cd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "7ac2eeac-bc53-9d81-c43f-5daa4f35f03e"], "hb3171950gce14g42dag92e7g284339ea3993": ["Leave this swamp. Never come back. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "8eeefe99-19e3-4b10-1dff-75b528c80981"], "h713b2cfbg93ecg4492gb118g6aaa25498e33": ["I have no time for this. I have a hag to kill. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "525e929e-3f27-6ccd-6624-40dbcaa0d57a"], "hef8ccafbgfbb6g4129g935cg5a56ddf376ad": ["What? You can't. She's a <i>hag.</i>", "08c970d7-3138-45e8-8965-68eadf4b07cd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "dd48530c-15f0-648d-8a4b-477f09293a62"], "h9f9f871fg80c0g4819ga381g9752bd647bf8": ["I got you away from Ethel. You're welcome.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "dc6374a9-abc3-17b4-caed-46cbcf174388"], "h97d84421g3cbag4beag9b3bg052c40462733": ["But where did she go? What is going on?", "08c970d7-3138-45e8-8965-68eadf4b07cd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "525836c3-5501-9b24-d8f9-47cea687d0e0"], "h539d6fa8gea1cg48a0gbf7ag13cd7c129c0f": ["You were eating pie with a hag. What did you expect?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "47ed19ce-08d2-efbc-6b2d-d7c43f83dc97"], "h8a3c0652g99abg443egac5agddc5301ee1a7": ["Not<i> this.</i>", "08c970d7-3138-45e8-8965-68eadf4b07cd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "75d276b2-34bd-0b55-9559-5aa5fe3a6693"], "h22551190g93d2g4d89g9b51g6f1765a81e8b": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hagspawn_SurrogateMother.html", "0b8ee657-190d-ed0f-7ae0-0d31538c712d"]}